Package com.eteks.awt.image

Class Summary
GIFDecoder An ImageProducer implementation that builds an image from a GIF input stream.
Web216ColorModel An example of IndexColorModel which uses a fixed palette consisting of the standard "safe 216 Web colors" + a tranparent color at index 216.
